These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade, mirinda
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, rowing, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is rowing is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | sprite | lemonade | mirinda   |
| Sport      | climbing    | rowing  | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, milk
There are 3 different nationalities: french, dutch, brazilian
1. the french is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the dutch is on the far left##1
3. the dutch is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | hot-chocolate     | milk      |
| Nationality   | dutch | french | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, coffee
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, orange
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating orange##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee  | sprite       |
| Food       | carrot     | cherry | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: plum, raspberry, banana
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, board-games, rock-climbing
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | banana    | raspberry     | plum |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | magic-tricks | board-games     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, chinchilla, cat
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, bus, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is the owner of the cat##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | chinchilla | dog     | cat |
| Transport   | snowmobile        | jet-ski | bus    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: apricot, cherry, carrot
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, car, ship
1. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person driving the car##1
3. the person eating carrot is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | carrot | apricot      | cherry  |
| Transport   | roller       | car | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, punk, metal
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, hamster, mouse
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the fan of punk is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | soul     | punk    |
| Pet           | hedgehog | mouse | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
