The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, photography, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
2. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | mango | lemon | pumpkin      |
| Hobby   | drawing     | traveling | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, photography, card-games
3 different pets are kept: lizard, goldfish, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the lizard is the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | card-games | photography | magic-tricks  |
| Pet     | guinea-pig     | lizard      | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, fanta
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, musical, fantasy
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | milk   | 7up    | fanta    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | scientific | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
