There are 3 different nationalities: indian, polish, american
1. the fan of techno is the indian##1
2. the indian is on the left of the fan of folk##1
3. the american is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | techno   | folk  |
| Nationality   | american    | indian | polish |

