.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: potato, plum, carrot
The people have 3 different jobs:  software-developer, chef, musician
1. the chef is on the right of the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating carrot is in the middle##1
3. the software-developer is on the right of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | potato     | carrot   | plum     |
| Job    | musician | chef | software-developer |

