.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, designer, architect
3 different pets are kept: hamster, cat, rat
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the architect##1
2. the architect is on the left of the designer##1
3. the designer is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | journalist    | architect | designer |
| Pet   | rat | hamster     | cat        |

