.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, water
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, reggae, hip-hop
1. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk  | water | fanta  |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | hip-hop   | soul |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-16::.
