1. the designer is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | sprite    |
| Job        | librarian    | security-guard | designer |

