.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, lawyer, analyst
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, japanese, russian
1. the russian is on the far left##1
2. the bartender is on the far right##1
3. the argentine is the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Job           | lawyer | analyst | bartender |
| Nationality   | russian  | argentine      | japanese |

