.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
There 3 different types of food: banana, broccoli, blueberry
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person eating banana is the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | broccoli | blueberry   | banana        |
| Sport   | swimming    | badminton | tennis |

