.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: peas, broccoli, garlic
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, skiing, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is skiing is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person eating peas##1
3. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | garlic | peas       | broccoli  |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | skiing | rugby |

 